flowchart LR
  A[Assemble source from pinned inputs]
  F[Freeze source-tree SHA-256]
  P[Select a later public beacon pulse]
  H[Derive post-freeze holdout seed]
  T[Run proofs, finite censuses, production contracts, contention, and performance gates]
  N[Run evaluator negative controls]
  M[Write source and evidence manifest]
  V1[Independent Python verifier]
  V2[Independent dependency-free Node.js verifier]
  Z[Build release ZIP]
  R[Extract and compare byte-for-byte]

  A --> F
  F --> P
  P --> H
  H --> T
  T --> N
  N --> M
  M --> V1
  M --> V2
  V1 --> Z
  V2 --> Z
  Z --> R
